Class AnonymousControllerTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.rmit.eres.seaports.controller.AnonymousControllerTest

  • @ContextConfiguration(value="/test-context.xml")
@Transactional
public class AnonymousControllerTest
extends java.lang.Object
    This test class holds tests against all the protected controllers methods performed by an anonymous user Most of the tests are expecting to get an "Access Denied" response.
